.hero
  .container
    .row
      .col
        .hero__text
          h1.font-green Looking for a Web Developer?
          h3.font-white I’m a web developer & UI designer from the Philippines. I make websites, usually with Wordpress.
  .mouse__container
    a(href="#about").mouse.button
      .scroller
  #particles-js

main.site-content
  section.about#about
    .container-fluid
      .row
        .col-12.px-0
          .profile-img__container
            .profile-img
              img(src='./assets/images/icon.jpg').img-fluid
        .col-12.px-0
          .content
            h1.content__header Hi, I’m Jason. Nice to meet you!
            h3.content__sub I started nearly 5 years ago, and from that time, I already made over hundreds of websites. From static websites to full Wordpress sites, you name it. I'm quietly confident, naturally curious, and perpetually improving my craft.
  section.skills#skills
    .container
      .row
        .col-12
          .content
            h1.content__header.text-center Things I'm good at
        .col-md-6.equal
          .content.content__first.content__border
            img(src='./assets/images/frontend-icon.png').content__image
            h2.content__sub Front-end Development
            p.content__text I create most of the websites that I made using Wordpress. I love to code things from scratch most of the time and enjoy bringing design ideas to life in the browser.
            h3.content__green Languages I speak:
            p.content__text HTML, CSS, Sass, PugJS, PHP, Javascript, jQuery, ReactJS.
            h3.content__green Dev tools that I use:
            ul.content__list
              each dev in ['Visual Studio Code', 'Wordpress', 'Woocommerce', 'Wordpress Theme Development', 'Bootstrap', 'Github', 'Bitbucket', 'Heroku', 'Codepen', 'Terminal', 'cPanel', 'mySQL']
                li.content__list--items= dev
        .col-md-6.equal
          .content.content__border
            img(src='./assets/images/design-icon.png').content__image
            h2.content__sub Graphic Design
            p.content__text I value simple content structure, clean design patterns, and thoughtful interactions. I believe in a minimalist approach towards design.
            h3.content__green Things I enjoy designing:
            p.content__text UI/UX, Web, Mobile, Apps, Branding, Social Media.
            h3.content__green Design tools that I use:
            ul.content__list
              each design in ['Adobe Photoshop', 'Adobe Illustrator', 'Adobe Experience Design', 'Adobe InDesign', 'Sketch', 'InvisionApp', 'Figma']
                li.content__list--items= design
  section.works#works
